2011-07-07T10:09:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/sigurd-microelec-june-sales-fall-16-18-table-6257-tt.html
SIGURD MICROELEC said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 16.18% to NT$360,833,000 from NT$430,472,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            360,833          430,472    
YOY%             -16.18%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,166,802        2,324,905   
YOY%              -6.80% 
=================================================================
 